<div class="center"><br />Amazing that it was so warm yesterday, and yet today is so cold!</div>
<p>We lucked out today: perhaps due to the snow, the Amphitheater Road was not yet open.  Even more impressive, we didn't see another cyclist on the entire outing.  Only three or so cars too.</p>
<p>Surprising if you ask me, as it really wasn't tremendously cold or even wet.  And the conditions were just magical.  Thanks to my usual cohort for joining!</p>
<p>I'm not ready for hot weather!!!</p>